```plantuml
@startuml
skinparam handwritten true

title 迭代器模式

note "集合，用于创建Iterator迭代器接口" as N1
note "会创建出具体的Iterator角色" as N2
note "具体的迭代器，\n包含了遍历集合所必须的信息（bookShelf）" as N3

interface Aggregate {
  + Iterator iterator()
}

interface Iterator<T> {
  + boolean hasNext()
  + T next()
}

class BookShelf {
  + BookIterator iterator()
}

class BookIterator<Book> {
  - BookShelf bookShelf
  + boolean hasNext()
  + Book next()
}

Aggregate -> Iterator : Creates >
Aggregate <|.. BookShelf
Iterator <|.. BookIterator
BookShelf o-right- BookIterator

N1 .. Aggregate
N2 .. BookShelf
N3 .. BookIterator

@enduml
```
